      "role": "user",
      "content": "hey i need some help. my neighbor just changed their wifi name to \"WE SEE YOU IN THE KITCHEN\" and honestly i'm getting really creeped out. like it's too specific. i also noticed that whenever i move from the living room to the bedroom the signal strength on my phone spikes way higher. do u think they're actually using their router to track where i am in my house?",
