      "role": "user",
      "content": "but how can it be \"interference\" if it only happens when I'm in specific spots? like, the signal was weak in the kitchen but the second I stepped toward the hallway it just went to full bars. and the name... \"WE SEE YOU IN THE KITCHEN\"... that's not just a coincidence. it feels like they are watching me through the signal itself. don't you think it's weird that a stranger would pick something that personal?",
