      "content": "a publicity stunt?? lol no way. they dont even know me. and the signal thing is what really bothers me... if it was just \"morbid humor\" it wouldn't be reacting to my physical location in the house. it feels like the signal is actually being modulated or something to follow me. if they are using some kind of advanced tech to do this, like signal triangulation or something, how would they even pull that off with just a standard router?",
